e":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"魏大勛","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Вэй Да Сюнь","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ngụy Đại Huân","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"魏大勳，原名魏興文，演員，畢業於中央戲劇學院 2007 級表演本科班。\n\n2008 年，出演個人首部電視劇《蘇菲日記》，從而正式進入演藝圈。2010 年，在革命歷史劇《毛岸英》中飾演毛岸青，從而受到關注 。2011 年，出演革命戰爭電影《辛亥革命》 。2012 年，主演諜戰劇《伏弩》。2013 年，主演校園青春情感劇《一又二分之一的夏天》。2014 年 5 月 23 日，魏大勳正式簽約傑偉品文化成為旗下籤約藝人；同年，主演家庭情感劇《因為愛情有幸福》。2015 年，獲得“亞洲影響力·東方盛典”最具潛力新人獎 。2016 年，在民國穿越劇《相愛穿梭千年 2：月光下的交換》中分別飾演男主角孫祺龍、張志剛。2017 年，合約到期成立個人工作室；同年，主演都市懸疑推理劇《超感》；10 月 27 日，其主演的愛情喜劇電影《因為愛情》上映。","name":"魏大勛","primary":false}}]}},"movie_857413_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1772689478565,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"}],"homepage":"","id":857413,"imdb_id":"tt2468610","origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_title":"美少年のまなざし","overview":"","popularity":0.1889,"poster_path":"/8kzFjaxUzyjsQ3QBHnPtm5Kdldd.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":34688,"logo_path":null,"name":"Nabe Cinema","origin_country":"JP"},{"id":138285,"logo_path":"/fjxX3f0XFIZYwUlpJkd4IAuNrWJ.png","name":"Okura Pictures","origin_country":"JP"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"JP","name":"Japan"}],"release_date":"2003-04-26","revenue":0,"runtime":61,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Japanese","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"美少年のまなざし","video":false,"vote_average":2,"vote_count":2}},"person_1168496_translations":{"at":1772689479508,"data":{"id":1168496,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Hotaru (ほたる) is a Japanese actress. While studying at Tama Art University, she began her acting career performing in an underground theater company. In 1993, she made her film debut in Mibōjin mofuku no modae (Widow: Bliss in a Mourning Dress), directed by Takahisa Zeze. Since then, she has appeared in numerous pink films, as well as independent films, direct-to-video films, and television dramas. In 2007, she left the theater company and changed her name to Hotaru. She made her directorial debut with the film Kisushite (Kiss Me), released at K's cinema in Shinjuku, Tokyo.","name":"Hotaru","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ほたる","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Hotaru (ほたる) es una actriz japonesa. Mientras estudiaba en Tama Art University, empezó su carrera como actriz actuando en una compañía de teatro underground. En 1993, hizo su debut cinematográfico en «Mibōjin mofuku no modae» (Widow: Bliss in a Mourning Dress), del director Takahisa Zeze. Desde entonces, ha aparecido en numerosas películas rosas (pink films), así como en películas independientes, cine directamente para vídeo y dramas televisivos. En 2007, dejó la compañía de teatro y cambió su nombre a Hotaru. Debutó como directora con el filme «Kisushite» (Bésame), estrenada en cines en el K's cinema de Shinjuku, Tokio.","name":"Hotaru","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"萤","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hotaru","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"螢","primary":false}}]}},"person_1635480_translations":{"at":1772689480782,"data":{"id":1635480,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Munehisa Sakurada","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"櫻田宗久","primary":true}}]}},"movie_1251478_keywords":{"at":1772689482917,"data":{"id":1251478,"keywords":[]}}}}